Stat Multiplier Scaling
Applies era stat bonus scaling up to level 37 and custom formula from 37 and above
- Below level 37: returns startValue
- At level 75+: returns endValue
- Between 37-74: linearly interpolates

This patch implements era-accurate stat-to-combat scaling for players based on level progression.
